# Local single-user web store — the dashboard's chats/settings/profile/API-keys/metrics/error-log
# (src/claymore/local_store.py). Defaults to ~/.claymore/ (outside the repo); these patterns cover
# a repo-relative CLAYMORE_LOCAL_DIR too. Holds real keys + lab chat history — never commit.
.claymore/
.claymore-local/
*.local.json

